lead_paragraph: Melo Trimble and Jake Layman scored 18 points each, and No. 14 Maryland closed out its home schedule with its best game in weeks, an 81-55 rout of Illinois on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 14 Maryland Blows Past Illinois 81-55 in Home Finale
